</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>蒙眼挑戰《隻狼》為防癌基金籌款，神級玩家兩小時高速爆機</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/20/speedrunner-beats-sekiro-in-2-hours-while-blindfolded/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=speedrunner-beats-sekiro-in-2-hours-while-blindfolded</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jan 2022 07:53:59 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[AGDQ 2022]]></category><category><![CDATA[Awesome Games Done Quick 2022]]></category><category><![CDATA[RTA]]></category><category><![CDATA[隻狼：暗影雙死]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1082029</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>大部份的遊戲迷應該都對 RTA （Real Time Attack）快速通關不陌生，但如果將難度提升到「極限」 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">大部份的遊戲迷應該都對 RTA （Real Time Attack）快速通關不陌生，但如果將難度提升到「極限」級別，蒙眼打機又是否可能？在剛完結的 Awesome Games Done Quick 2022 競速破關馬拉松活動中，就有挑戰者以蒙眼方式，兩小時就通關遊戲《隻狼：暗影雙死》。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1082030" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/43FBBDA7-7FAB-4885-B66A-FEE7CBD4A64E-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/43FBBDA7-7FAB-4885-B66A-FEE7CBD4A64E-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/43FBBDA7-7FAB-4885-B66A-FEE7CBD4A64E-1280x721.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/43FBBDA7-7FAB-4885-B66A-FEE7CBD4A64E-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/43FBBDA7-7FAB-4885-B66A-FEE7CBD4A64E-1536x865.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/43FBBDA7-7FAB-4885-B66A-FEE7CBD4A64E-2048x1153.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/43FBBDA7-7FAB-4885-B66A-FEE7CBD4A64E.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">AGDQ 2022 因疫情影響以全網上形式舉行，釋出了不少玩家的參賽最快影片。當中最為矚目的莫過於挑戰者 Mitchriz 以蒙眼方式挑戰難度極高的遊戲《隻狼：暗影雙死》，他單靠耳聽的提示，在兩小時三十五秒完成通關，創下了賽事的新紀錄。Mitchriz 去年就曾挑戰過矇眼速通《隻狼》，當時他花了將近 5 小時，如今在這次慈善大會上，他從 NEW GAME 開始一路到修羅結局全破，時間不到去年的一半，可謂是進步神速！</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1082031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/CD485ED8-2134-45DC-B125-5A5571CD69F3-694x396.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/CD485ED8-2134-45DC-B125-5A5571CD69F3-694x396.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/CD485ED8-2134-45DC-B125-5A5571CD69F3-1280x731.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/CD485ED8-2134-45DC-B125-5A5571CD69F3-768x439.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/CD485ED8-2134-45DC-B125-5A5571CD69F3-1536x877.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/CD485ED8-2134-45DC-B125-5A5571CD69F3-2048x1170.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/CD485ED8-2134-45DC-B125-5A5571CD69F3.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">要完成蒙眼挑戰當然需要大量的練習及記憶力，過程中 Mitchriz 利用音效來確認自己的位置與角色的面對方向，又會利用貼牆的動作音效來定位自己的動作、揮砍來橫移；十分聰明地活用墊步計算距離，和佛渡回歸作為儲存點。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_81726"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FQeeRBtQgzE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在比賽結束後，官方宣佈 AGDQ 2022 為預防癌症基金會籌集了 3,416,729 美元（約港幣 2,660 萬元）。自活動成立 12 年以來，AGDQ 已經籌集了超過 3400 萬美元（約港幣 2.6 億元） Games Done Quick 賽事的創紀錄總數。根據統計，最高捐款的金額為 236,656 美元。 AGDQ 2022 也成為了最快達到 100 萬美元（約港幣 780 萬元）捐款的 GDQ 活動。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">🏁TIME 🏁<br /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/AGDQ2022?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#AGDQ2022</a> has raised a total amount of $3,416,729 for <a href="https://twitter.com/preventcancer?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@preventcancer</a>! This is officially the most we&#39;ve ever raised in the history of <a href="https://twitter.com/GamesDoneQuick?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@GamesDoneQuick</a> &#8211; ANOTHER WR🏆<br />Thank you to everyone who made this marathon possible, and thank you all for your generosity &amp; support❤️</p><p>&mdash; Games Done Quick (@GamesDoneQuick) <a href="https://twitter.com/GamesDoneQuick/status/1482609194263990275?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 16, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://youtu.be/FQeeRBtQgzE">YouTube</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
